data.description: ACTIVE UNDER CONTRACT - ACCEPTING BACK UP OFFERS  Here's a fantastic opportunity for you! This spacious 4-BEDROOM POOL home, offering 1,632 square feet of living space, is nestled on a large lot in a peaceful CUL-DE-SAC. Picture yourself enjoying the privacy of a FENCED YARD with a no-build area behind, a convenient storage shed, and a 2-car garage. The highlight? A spacious SCREEN-ENCLOSED LANAI with a refreshing POOL, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. With a total square footage under the roof reaching 2,579, you'll have plenty of room to stretch out and enjoy life. Updates? You got it! The AC system was replaced in 2016, and the roof in 2015. Plus, a new hot water heater was added in 2015, and a hurricane-rated garage door installed in 2021, ensuring your comfort and safety. Let's talk about luxury. The primary bedroom features a generous walk-in closet and a private bathroom with a walk-in shower. And don't miss the kitchen, boasting newer appliances and a large window overlooking the pool area. Need more space for outdoor living? The lanai offers over 300 square feet of covered space, complete with a convenient bar area. There's even a large screen-enclosed front porch for those relaxing evenings. Worried about yard maintenance? Fear not! A sprinkler system and irrigation well make keeping your yard lush and green both easy and affordable. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to own your dream home! NO HOA OR CDD!
